Class IncidentImpl

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.BaseObjectImpl
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.IncidentImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SonarObject, Incident, Storable
public class IncidentImpl extends BaseObjectImpl implements Incident
An incident is an event (crash, stall, etc.) which has an effect on traffic.
Author:
Douglas Lau
